        <div class="b_header loyalty_header"> 
            <h1 class="b_width">With us, you save a<br>minimum of 15% more than<br>any other pet shop out there</h1>
			<div class="switcher">
				<div class="b_width">
					<a class="active">Loyalty Programs</a>
					<a href="pay_it_forward">Pay it Forward</a>
				</div>
			</div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="b_comment">We don’t claim to be the biggest, nor do we claim to have more brand then others but we do claim and confirm that by doing your pet shopping with us, you save a minimum of 15% more then any other pet shop out there. You can even have a chance to have all your monthly shopping done free of charge.<br><br>Now the real question is, how can we save 25% on our shopping? Or how is possible to shop for free? With our 4 fixed and ongoing loyalty program, the above has become a reality for the first time ever.
        </p>
        
		<button class="control left" id="left_loyalty"><img src="<%= asset_path 'loyalty/6-a.svg' %>"></button>
		<button class="control right" id="right_loyalty"><img src="<%= asset_path 'loyalty/6-a-2.svg' %>"></button>
		
