            </div>
            
            <div class="loyalty_item">
                <img id="bird" src="<%= asset_path 'loyalty/pets/loyalty-3.jpg' %>">
                <p>Loyalty Program<span>3</span></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="loyalty_item">
                <img src="<%= asset_path 'loyalty/pets/loyalty-4.jpg' %>">
                <p>Loyalty Program<span>4</span></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="loyalty_item">
                <img id="rabbit" src="<%= asset_path 'loyalty/pets/loyalty-5.jpg' %>">
                <p>Loyalty Program<span>5</span></p>
            </div>
            
        </div>
        
        <div class="b_width info_container" id="info_container">
            
            <ul class="loyalty_info active">
                <li>Spend between AED 0 to 500 and get a <span>WHOPPING 3%</span> cash back to your account</li>
                <li>Spend between AED 500 to 1,000 and get a <span>CRAZY 5%</span> cash back to your account</li>
                <li>Spend AED 1,000 to 2,000 and get the <span>UNBELIEVABLE 7.5%</span> cash back to your account</li>
                <li>And if you have a big pet family and have to spend more than 2,000 well you will get the <span>JACKPOT of 10%</span> cash back</li>
            </ul>
			
			<ul class="loyalty_info">
				<li>Get rewarded again on your spends with our yearly loyalty program.</li>
				<li>Spend AED 5,000 to AED 10,000 between Jan 1st and Dec 31st and get an <span>additional 3% back</span></li>
				<li>Spends AED 10,000 + between Jan 1st and Dec 31st and get an <span>additional 5% back</span></li>
            </ul>
			
			<ul class="loyalty_info">
				<li>With every order we send you <span>free Toys, Treats, Accessories & Food</span></li>
            </ul>
			
			<ul class="loyalty_info">
				<li>At the end of every month we do an online raffle draw where 25 of our shopping members will be selected randomly and will each win <span>AED 100 cash back</span> to their account</li>
            </ul>
			
			<ul class="loyalty_info">
				<li>Receive Cash to your account for your <span>pets birthday</span></li>
            </ul>
            
        </div>
        
        <div class="b_width terms">
            
            <p>Terms & Conditions:</p>
            
            <ul>
                <li>Loyalty Program 1 & 2 are not valid on discounted items or discount codes</li>
                <li>Points can not be transferred between accounts</li>
                <li>If no orders have been made for a 6 month period, all previous points will expire</li>
                <li>Free delivery on any order above AED 100. AED 20 delivery charge will apply for orders less then AED 100.</li>
            </ul>
            
        </div>
		
